    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Roof-like coverings, usually of canvas or metal and often adjustable, placed over windows, doors, or decks to provide protection from sun and rain.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
